Package com.paypal.sdk.profiles

Interface Summary
APIProfile Interface which defines the information PayPal needs to know about a merchant in order to provide API services.
EWPProfile Interface which defines the information PayPal needs to know about a merchant in order to provide Encrypted Website Payment (EWP) services.
ProfileHandler Stores and retrieves profiles by interfacing with external storage device
 

Class Summary
BaseAPIProfile Base implementation for the API Profile.
CertificateAPIProfile API Profile with SSL Certificate.
DefaultEWPProfile Default implementation of an EWP Profile
DefaultProfileHandler Stores profiles in a serialized data file
PermissionAPIProfile  
ProfileFactory Utility class used to create profile objects.
Profiles Data class that maintains the API and EWP profiles that are in memory.
ProfilesManager Singleton class that acts as central access point for profile management.
SignatureAPIProfile API Profile with Signature.
UniPayAPIProfile API Profile with UniPay.
XMLProfileHandler XML implementation of ProfileHandler which stores profile data in an external XML file
